summary.description:
Today, a bit warmer for the feels like temperature (up 3.0°C) and outside temperature (up 2.4°C) and more moisture-laden outside humidity (up 7%) and rainfall (up 1.5 mm).

Compared to today, yesterday also had noticeable differences in cloud levels (up 511 m) and pressure (up 9 mbar).

The past week and month had observable variation in feels like temperature (up 38.9°C), outside temperature (up 40.9°C), dew point temperature (up 36.2°C), and cloud levels (up 919 m) when compared to today.
